00:53:08.384 --> 00:53:12.754
If Dad finds out, he'll kick us out and have Yong Gil thrown in jail.

00:53:14.224 --> 00:53:15.394
Is that what you're afraid of?

00:53:16.354 --> 00:53:17.424
He is still...

00:53:18.164 --> 00:53:20.224
Ji Hu's father, you know.

00:53:40.184 --> 00:53:42.184
(Seung Hui Hair Salon)

00:53:47.654 --> 00:53:49.494
Where on earth did you go, Hui Gyeong?

00:53:51.124 --> 00:53:53.094
(For rent)

00:53:55.634 --> 00:53:57.064
You're unbelievable, Gong Dae Han.

00:53:57.964 --> 00:54:00.004
How can I be hungry at a time like this?

00:54:02.434 --> 00:54:05.044
(Seong Tae Realty)

00:54:05.104 --> 00:54:07.144
She was thrilled that a good person was taking over.

00:54:07.204 --> 00:54:08.644
- Really? - Yes.

00:54:08.974 --> 00:54:12.314
- My gosh, I'm so excited! - I'm sure you'll do great.

00:54:13.284 --> 00:54:14.544
Yes, Aunt.

00:54:15.014 --> 00:54:18.124
Hi, I'm Hui Gyeong's mother-in-law over in Onjeong.

00:54:19.554 --> 00:54:22.794
I should have come in person, but things have been so busy.

00:54:22.954 --> 00:54:24.324
So, how are you feeling?

00:54:24.794 --> 00:54:26.024
Me? Why do you ask?

00:54:26.924 --> 00:54:27.924
Pardon?

00:54:28.864 --> 00:54:31.264
I'd heard you were unwell.

00:54:32.164 --> 00:54:33.604
The kids went down to see you.

00:54:34.774 --> 00:54:36.804
I must've gotten it wrong.

00:54:40.374 --> 00:54:41.374
I see.

00:54:43.214 --> 00:54:45.414
Oh, so just Dae Han came by.

00:54:47.284 --> 00:54:49.184
All right, I understand.

00:55:03.464 --> 00:55:04.694
Yes, ma'am.

00:55:05.164 --> 00:55:07.204
I was just about to call you, actually.

00:55:07.464 --> 00:55:10.804
Did you happen to speak with my son yesterday or today?

00:55:11.134 --> 00:55:13.874
No, he hasn't called me.

00:55:14.474 --> 00:55:17.044
I see. So, what were you calling about?

00:55:17.114 --> 00:55:20.844
If you're not taking the house, I have another client interested.

00:55:21.984 --> 00:55:25.084
Yes, I suppose you should.

00:55:28.824 --> 00:55:31.354
- Welcome. - Hi.

00:55:31.764 --> 00:55:34.794
Can I get a bottle of soju and the usual, please?

00:55:35.294 --> 00:55:36.864
How come you're alone today?

00:55:37.334 --> 00:55:40.764
- You're always so lovey-dovey here. - Tell me about it.

00:55:42.034 --> 00:55:43.174
Excuse me.

00:55:43.474 --> 00:55:46.904
- Another bottle of soju over here! - Coming.

00:55:58.624 --> 00:55:59.684
Yes, Mom.

00:56:00.924 --> 00:56:03.394
I'm almost home. Yes.

00:56:05.164 --> 00:56:08.594
I'm meeting a friend for a drink, so don't wait up.

00:56:09.494 --> 00:56:11.964
Okay. What?

00:56:12.304 --> 00:56:14.464
Of course. Hui Gyeong is doing fine.

00:56:16.004 --> 00:56:18.504
Yes. Don't worry, just get some sleep.

00:56:19.674 --> 00:56:20.704
Okay.

00:56:44.634 --> 00:56:48.164
- What are you doing? - Weren't you meeting a friend?

00:56:48.804 --> 00:56:49.834
Isn't that me?

00:56:50.904 --> 00:56:53.604
Who are you? I don't share tables with strangers.

00:56:55.314 --> 00:56:57.644
- You don't recognize me, sweetie? - "Sweetie?"

00:56:57.944 --> 00:57:00.284
That's creepy. You look way older than me.

00:57:01.514 --> 00:57:05.454
It's me, Dong Suk. I lived across the street from you,

00:57:05.524 --> 00:57:08.184
and I still work just across the road...

00:57:08.254 --> 00:57:10.754
at the Korean medicine clinic.

00:57:10.824 --> 00:57:13.524
I'm Yang Dong Suk!

00:57:13.994 --> 00:57:15.234
And? So what?

00:57:17.094 --> 00:57:21.634
Remember how you'd carry my bag on the way to piano lessons?

00:57:22.874 --> 00:57:26.574
You said it dragged on the ground because I was too short,

00:57:26.644 --> 00:57:29.044
so you carried it for me every day.

00:57:29.844 --> 00:57:33.744
I don't think we're close enough to be reminiscing like this.

00:57:35.784 --> 00:57:37.584
Just because we had a falling-out,

00:57:38.214 --> 00:57:40.584
it doesn't mean the memories just disappear.

00:57:41.954 --> 00:57:43.524
Look, if you're this drunk, you should just go home.

00:57:44.824 --> 00:57:45.894
Fine, I get it.

00:57:47.894 --> 00:57:52.534
Getting blown off wherever I go. That's my life for you.

00:57:53.664 --> 00:57:55.274
Fine, I'll go.

00:57:56.304 --> 00:57:57.904
Hey!

00:57:58.204 --> 00:58:01.744
What's with you? Hey, careful. Sit down.

00:58:03.814 --> 00:58:06.984
Why are you getting wasted alone? What about your husband?

00:58:07.114 --> 00:58:08.114
Ji Hu's dad?

00:58:10.014 --> 00:58:11.054
He ran off.

00:58:11.824 --> 00:58:12.824
What?

00:58:12.884 --> 00:58:16.024
I thought he was scared of getting kicked out,

00:58:16.024 --> 00:58:17.594
but he took off on his own.

00:58:18.424 --> 00:58:19.924
And this time,

00:58:20.624 --> 00:58:21.894
as if losing all our money wasn't enough,

00:58:22.164 --> 00:58:24.094
he even stooped to stealing.

00:58:27.464 --> 00:58:28.634
You've really been through it...

00:58:30.704 --> 00:58:33.544
So what about you, Gong Dae Han? Why are you drinking alone?

00:58:39.214 --> 00:58:40.514
You know...

00:58:44.314 --> 00:58:47.054
Did you know your wife is cheating on you?

00:58:50.324 --> 00:58:52.894
- What did you say? - I heard the whole thing.

00:58:53.294 --> 00:58:56.734
Your wife on the phone with her lover.

00:58:57.264 --> 00:58:58.294
You...

00:58:59.064 --> 00:59:00.504
Watch your mouth.

00:59:00.834 --> 00:59:03.074
My Hui Gyeong is not like that, you hear me?

00:59:03.704 --> 00:59:04.934
But it's true.

00:59:05.604 --> 00:59:08.744
"It feels like a dream, darling."

00:59:09.414 --> 00:59:10.414
That's what she said.

00:59:12.944 --> 00:59:15.384
When she's with you,

00:59:15.454 --> 00:59:18.154
she calls you "honey," right? But she said...

00:59:18.784 --> 00:59:21.584
"My dear husband has no idea."

00:59:21.954 --> 00:59:25.094
- "See you tomorrow, darling." - Hey!

00:59:25.164 --> 00:59:27.394
- You scared me! - I've had enough of you... Darn it.

00:59:27.564 --> 00:59:29.034
What are you yelling for?

00:59:40.504 --> 00:59:41.844
Yes, Officer Jung.

00:59:41.874 --> 00:59:44.114
Yes, hi. Sorry it took me a while to get back to you.

00:59:44.374 --> 00:59:46.444
I've been canvassing the area all day.

00:59:46.584 --> 00:59:49.984
Don't worry about it. I appreciate you looking into this.

00:59:51.054 --> 00:59:54.424
Well, I wasn't able to find your wife.

00:59:54.754 --> 00:59:56.994
But I did find a lead.

00:59:57.394 --> 00:59:58.824
- A lead? - Yes.

00:59:59.024 --> 01:00:01.594
I'm at the convenience store where I shop often.

01:00:01.834 --> 01:00:05.064
Apparently, the owner overheard Ms. Lee Hui Gyeong...

01:00:05.064 --> 01:00:07.064
talking on the phone with someone.

01:00:07.704 --> 01:00:10.974
Who was she on the phone with?

01:00:11.034 --> 01:00:13.274
No, I mean, what did she say?

01:00:14.004 --> 01:00:17.344
Well, the thing is...

01:00:17.774 --> 01:00:20.144
It's all right. Just tell me, Officer Jung.

01:00:20.384 --> 01:00:23.084
Apparently, this is what she said.

01:00:23.814 --> 01:00:27.184
"Pick me up at the convenience store at Gongsan Junction, darling."

01:00:28.824 --> 01:00:29.824
What...

01:00:30.794 --> 01:00:33.024
- "Darling?" - See?

01:00:33.494 --> 01:00:36.234
I told you she said "darling."

01:00:38.094 --> 01:00:39.264
Well...

01:00:41.404 --> 01:00:45.544
- Are you sure? - Yes. The store owner...

01:00:46.174 --> 01:00:49.214
showed me CCTV footage of her getting into a car.

01:00:49.714 --> 01:00:52.614
It's a bit grainy, so you can't see the face, but...

01:00:52.944 --> 01:00:56.454
it looks like she left with a man.

01:00:56.954 --> 01:00:57.954
I see.

01:00:59.454 --> 01:01:02.594
I understand. Okay, all right.

01:01:16.834 --> 01:01:18.604
You should have known better.

01:01:19.774 --> 01:01:24.614
You're from a family of doctors, and you're a physical therapist.

01:01:25.444 --> 01:01:28.584
Why marry a girl with no background, who's not even in your league,

01:01:28.654 --> 01:01:31.484
all because she's pretty?

01:01:44.364 --> 01:01:45.964
At least I'm better off.

01:01:47.864 --> 01:01:51.274
Ji Hu's dad... At least he never cheated.

01:01:57.914 --> 01:01:59.084
Dae Han?

01:02:00.614 --> 01:02:01.614
- Hey, Seong Mi. - My gosh.

01:02:02.214 --> 01:02:04.054
- What... - I...

01:02:04.584 --> 01:02:07.554
- My goodness. - The person I respect the most.

01:02:07.624 --> 01:02:12.524
Goodness, you've had a lot to drink. Didn't Hui Gyeong visit her family?

01:02:12.764 --> 01:02:13.764
Yes.

01:02:15.334 --> 01:02:16.334
Seong Mi.

01:02:17.234 --> 01:02:18.394
I'm so sorry.

01:02:19.364 --> 01:02:20.934
I'm really sorry.

01:02:21.904 --> 01:02:23.634
What are you sorry for?

01:02:24.004 --> 01:02:25.644
I'm pretty sure Hui Gyeong...

01:02:27.674 --> 01:02:29.544
might have run off with the money.

01:02:30.644 --> 01:02:33.384
- What? - I think she was seeing someone.

01:02:34.144 --> 01:02:38.184
- Wait, what are you talking about? - Hui Gyeong was having an affair.

01:02:39.124 --> 01:02:41.254
She had an affair and ran off behind my back.

01:02:42.294 --> 01:02:43.624
She was cheating on me.

01:02:44.294 --> 01:02:46.964
She just up and left. Just like my father...

01:02:47.294 --> 01:02:48.324
She just...

01:02:48.324 --> 01:02:49.334
Dae Han.

01:02:52.264 --> 01:02:54.134
Seong Mi, wait. Seong Mi...

01:02:54.964 --> 01:02:56.074
I have a favor to ask.

01:02:57.534 --> 01:03:00.944
Promise not to tell Mom and Jeong Han. Okay?

01:03:01.404 --> 01:03:03.874
If Mom and Jeong Han find out, they'll be heartbroken...

01:03:06.984 --> 01:03:10.754
Mom might collapse again, so please just keep it a secret.

01:03:11.754 --> 01:03:13.184
Collapse over what?

01:03:47.784 --> 01:03:50.394
(Recipe for Love)

01:03:50.454 --> 01:03:53.794
When I was little, a friend was going to study abroad,

01:03:53.864 --> 01:03:55.494
so I made this as a farewell gift.

01:03:55.564 --> 01:03:58.234
By any chance, was that person your first love, Ju Ah?

01:03:59.564 --> 01:04:02.934
Dr. Gong was treating Dr. Yang like a bratty little kid,

01:04:03.004 --> 01:04:04.074
and just bullying him relentlessly.

01:04:04.134 --> 01:04:07.004
That's rich, from the one begging for a job.

01:04:07.144 --> 01:04:08.844
You have proof?

01:04:08.914 --> 01:04:12.584
Someone recently taught me the importance of having proof.

01:04:12.784 --> 01:04:15.884
You absolutely have to get Dr. Gong's phone.

01:04:16.154 --> 01:04:18.784
Float like a butterfly, sting like a bee.

01:04:18.954 --> 01:04:21.884
You have to get a divorce. You can't go on like this.

01:04:22.594 --> 01:04:24.024
I don't recognize this number.

01:04:26.224 --> 01:04:27.464
Hello? Who is this?